lynette, if i close my eyes
even for a moment,

730
00:39:59,858 --> 00:40:01,944
it's because of these
antihistamines i've been taking.

731
00:40:01,944 --> 00:40:03,111
really?

732
00:40:03,111 --> 00:40:05,739
is that why you passed out
on your front lawn

733
00:40:05,739 --> 00:40:07,533
yesterday morning?

734
00:40:07,574 --> 00:40:10,536
now that you're speaking to me
in a fairly accusatory tone,

735
00:40:10,577 --> 00:40:13,038
may i remind you that
i was doing you a favor?

736
00:40:13,038 --> 00:40:15,541
you put my kids in danger,
and then you lied about it.

737
00:40:15,541 --> 00:40:17,543
doou not get
how big that is?

738
00:40:17,543 --> 00:40:19,545
do you have some
kind of problem with alcohol?

739
00:40:19,545 --> 00:40:21,463
no! the only problem i have
is with your children.

740
00:40:21,463 --> 00:40:23,924
they're incorrigible
because you let them run amok.

741
00:40:23,966 --> 00:40:25,425
and if i hadn't
drifted off,

742
00:40:25,467 --> 00:40:27,594
they would have waited
until i was in the bathroom

743
00:40:27,636 --> 00:40:29,930
or stuck on the phone
or upstairs doing laundry.

744
00:40:31,223 --> 00:40:32,891
on any given day,

745
00:40:32,933 --> 00:40:36,019
how many glasses of wine
do you put away?

746
00:40:39,106 --> 00:40:41,567
i will not be spoken to
like that.

747
00:40:41,608 --> 00:40:43,277
i just won't.

748
00:40:46,613 --> 00:40:48,282
(sighs)

749
00:40:57,708 --> 00:40:59,710
(bottles clanking)

750
00:41:02,754 --> 00:41:05,674
<i>now and then,
we allneed a little help...</i>

751
00:41:08,177 --> 00:41:11,638
<i>so we ask for small favors.</i>

752
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:14,433
thanks. i owe you one.

753
00:41:14,474 --> 00:41:15,934
<i>but it's always best</i>

754
00:41:15,976 --> 00:41:19,271
<i>to be wary of those eager
to come to our rescue.</i>

755
00:41:19,271 --> 00:41:21,607
well, go on.
kiss the bride.

756
00:41:24,276 --> 00:41:26,278
(chuckles)

757
00:41:28,155 --> 00:41:30,574
<i>because even the smallest
of favors...</i>

758
00:41:30,574 --> 00:41:34,578
sure thing, tom. i'd be happy
to baby-sit for you.

759
00:41:34,578 --> 00:41:37,873
my, have you noticed
how clogged my rain gutters are?

760
00:41:37,873 --> 00:41:40,626
...carries a price tag.

761
00:41:40,667 --> 00:41:43,378
<i>yes, everyone has an agenda.</i>

762
00:41:43,420 --> 00:41:45,339
i heard about your operation,
aunt inez,

763
00:41:45,339 --> 00:41:47,341
and i'm jumping
on a plane right now

764
00:41:47,382 --> 00:41:49,343
to come and help you out.

765
00:41:49,384 --> 00:41:51,345
<i>no matter what
they may tell us.</i>

766
00:41:51,386 --> 00:41:53,555
no, i'm happy to,

767
00:41:53,597 --> 00:41:58,477
and i'm prepared to stay
as long as it takes.

768
00:41:58,519 --> 00:42:00,729
<i>and in those rare instances</i>

769
00:42:00,771 --> 00:42:03,982
<i>"where there" is
no ulterior motive,</i>

770
00:42:04,024 --> 00:42:05,651
<i>we're so taken aback</i>

771
00:42:05,692 --> 00:42:08,445
<i>that we may fail
to recognize the truth...</i>

772
00:42:21,667 --> 00:42:26,964
<i>that a loving friend has just
done us an enormous favor.</i>

773
